data.description: Welcome to the historic Pasture Point neighborhood in Downtown Hampton. This charming Victorian style home has 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths and is nearly 1,400 sqft. Inside you will find original hardwood floors throughout the main level, a gorgeous built in bookshelf and lots of natural lighting throughout the home. Take a minute to relax and feel the breeze on your front porch swing or enjoy the back covered porch out behind your newly installed privacy fence. New Roof installed in 2021. This is a great opportunity to live minutes from downtown Hampton, Langley Air Force Base, Buckroe Beach, shops and much more. Call today to see this one!
